item.title: My newest Stuff
item.dc:creator: @GMAN7 GMAN7
item.description:
@GMAN7 wrote:

#1. The first uses a render lol… And I didn’t just “slap” anything anywhere…
#2. I’m not much of a fan of the second either lol… But I don’t rate them I just make them.
#3. Not all that different from the original stock? Nope, just the smudging, Clip masking, C4ds, MORE SMUDGING, The Lines are just a touch… If you read the TuT, They’re optional…
#4. How did you think the first was a stock? It uses a stock image with Glass layering and displacements as a BG… They aren’t connected at all… lol.
